---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Navigation from '../../components/Navigation.astro';
---

<Layout title="願景 | 光禾華德福">
  <Navigation />
  
  <section class="hero-small">
    <div class="container">
      <h1>光禾的願景</h1>
      <p>我們對教育的期待與展望</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section">
    <div class="container">
      
      <div class="vision-block">
        <div class="vision-item">
          <div class="number">1</div>
          <div class="content">
            <h3>愛與榜樣</h3>
            <p>一群有志成人以「愛與榜樣」姿態，讓孩子在一個有界線但自由的環境下學習與成長。</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="vision-item">
          <div class="number">2</div>
          <div class="content">
            <h3>自我實現與社會承擔</h3>
            <p>透過華德福十二年一貫課程，培養孩子擁有「自我實現與承擔社會需要」的能力。</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="vision-item">
          <div class="number">3</div>
          <div class="content">
            <h3>身心靈的教育</h3>
            <p>讓社群的每個人辨識身心靈的教育，並且平衡與健康我們的生命。</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

    </div>
  </section>

  <footer class="footer">
    <div class="container">
      <p>© 2026 光禾華德福實驗學校. All rights reserved.</p>
    </div>
  </footer>
</Layout>

<style>
  .hero-small {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #8B4513, #228B22);
    color: white;
    padding: 4rem 2rem;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .hero-small h1 { font-size: 3rem; margin-bottom: 0.5rem; }
  .hero-small p { font-size: 1.2rem; opacity: 0.9; }

  .section { padding: 4rem 2rem; }
  .container { max-width: 800px; margin: 0 auto; }

  .vision-block {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 2rem;
  }

  .vision-item {
    display: flex;
    gap: 1.5rem;
    background: white;
    padding: 2rem;
    border-radius: 20px;
    box-shadow: 0 10px 40px rgba(139,69,19,0.1);
    align-items: flex-start;
  }

  .number {
    width: 50px;
    height: 50px;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #FF8C00, #FFD700);
    border-radius: 50%;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    color: white;
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    font-weight: bold;
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }

  .content h3 {
    color: #8B4513;
    margin: 0 0 0.5rem 0;
  }

  .content p {
    color: #666;
    margin: 0;
    line-height: 1.8;
  }

  .footer { background: #333; color: white; padding: 2rem; text-align: center; margin-top: 2rem; }
</style>
